Nippon Mining cuts copper price by 10 , 000 yen . Nippon Mining and Metals Co said on Thursday it had cut its selling price for electrolytic copper by 10 , 000 yen to 320 , 000 yen per tonne , effective immediately . Major Japanese smelters periodically review their selling prices , changing them in line with market prices and currency rates . - - Tokyo Commodity Desk + 81 - 3 - 3432 - 7431 
